{
  "video_id": "6V6p1tgHfm0",
  "title": "How to have better political conversations | Robb Willer",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Joanna Pietrulewicz"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 15636.0,
      "text": "So you probably have the sense, as most people do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15660.0,
      "end_time": 19316.0,
      "text": "that polarization is getting worse in our country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19340.0,
      "end_time": 22796.0,
      "text": "that the divide between the left and the right"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22820.0,
      "end_time": 26356.0,
      "text": "is as bad as it&#39;s been in really any of our lifetimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26380.0,
      "end_time": 31660.0,
      "text": "But you might also reasonably wonder if research backs up your intuition."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32380.000000000004,
      "end_time": 37600.0,
      "text": "And in a nutshell, the answer is sadly yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38740.0,
      "end_time": 40756.0,
      "text": "In study after study, we find"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40780.0,
      "end_time": 44460.0,
      "text": "that liberals and conservatives have grown further apart."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 50360.0,
      "text": "They increasingly wall themselves off in these ideological silos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50600.0,
      "end_time": 54196.0,
      "text": "consuming different news, talking only to like-minded others"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54220.0,
      "end_time": 57460.0,
      "text": "and more and more choosing to live in different parts of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 58540.0,
      "end_time": 61756.0,
      "text": "And I think that most alarming of all of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 61780.0,
      "end_time": 65580.0,
      "text": "is seeing this rising animosity on both sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 67916.0,
      "text": "Liberals and conservatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67940.0,
      "end_time": 69836.0,
      "text": "Democrats and Republicans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69860.0,
      "end_time": 72980.0,
      "text": "more and more they just don&#39;t like one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 74140.0,
      "end_time": 76156.0,
      "text": "You see it in many different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76180.0,
      "end_time": 79836.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t want to befriend one another. They don&#39;t want to date one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79860.0,
      "end_time": 83156.0,
      "text": "If they do, if they find out, they find each other less attractive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83180.0,
      "end_time": 86276.0,
      "text": "and they more and more don&#39;t want their children to marry someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86300.0,
      "end_time": 87996.0,
      "text": "who supports the other party,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88200.0,
      "end_time": 89780.0,
      "text": "a particularly shocking statistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 91460.0,
      "end_time": 94276.0,
      "text": "You know, in my lab, the students that I work with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94300.0,
      "end_time": 97756.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re talking about some sort of social pattern --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97780.0,
      "end_time": 101316.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a movie buff, and so I&#39;m often like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101340.0,
      "end_time": 104300.0,
      "text": "what kind of movie are we in here with this pattern?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104900.0,
      "end_time": 108180.0,
      "text": "So what kind of movie are we in with political polarization?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108900.0,
      "end_time": 111620.0,
      "text": "Well, it could be a disaster movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 112700.0,
      "end_time": 114380.0,
      "text": "It certainly seems like a disaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114740.0,
      "end_time": 116740.0,
      "text": "Could be a war movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117460.0,
      "end_time": 118660.0,
      "text": "Also fits."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119300.0,
      "end_time": 123116.0,
      "text": "But what I keep thinking is that we&#39;re in a zombie apocalypse movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 123140.0,
      "end_time": 124596.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124620.0,
      "end_time": 126916.0,
      "text": "Right? You know the kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126940.0,
      "end_time": 129356.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s people wandering around in packs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129380.0,
      "end_time": 131156.0,
      "text": "not thinking for themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131180.0,
      "end_time": 132796.0,
      "text": "seized by this mob mentality"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132820.0,
      "end_time": 136600.0,
      "text": "trying to spread their disease and destroy society."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137300.0,
      "end_time": 139636.0,
      "text": "And you probably think, as I do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139660.0,
      "end_time": 143116.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re the good guy in the zombie apocalypse movie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 143140.0,
      "end_time": 146835.0,
      "text": "and all this hate and polarization, it&#39;s being propagated by the other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 146860.0,
      "end_time": 148740.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;re Brad Pitt, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 149580.0,
      "end_time": 152476.0,
      "text": "Free-thinking, righteous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 152500.0,
      "end_time": 154796.0,
      "text": "just trying to hold on to what we hold dear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154820.0,
      "end_time": 158396.0,
      "text": "you know, not foot soldiers in the army of the undead."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158420.0,
      "end_time": 159875.0,
      "text": "Not that."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 159900.0,
      "end_time": 161100.0,
      "text": "Never that."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 161900.0,
      "end_time": 163396.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 163420.0,
      "end_time": 166140.0,
      "text": "what movie do you suppose they think they&#39;re in?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167300.0,
      "end_time": 168516.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168540.0,
      "end_time": 171760.0,
      "text": "Well, they absolutely think that they&#39;re the good guys"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171100.0,
      "end_time": 172956.0,
      "text": "in the zombie apocalypse movie. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172980.0,
      "end_time": 175956.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;d better believe that they think that they&#39;re Brad Pitt"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175980.0,
      "end_time": 178100.0,
      "text": "and that we, we are the zombies."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 180940.0,
      "end_time": 183300.0,
      "text": "And who&#39;s to say that they&#39;re wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 184260.0,
      "end_time": 187380.0,
      "text": "I think that the truth is that we&#39;re all a part of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188600.0,
      "end_time": 191220.0,
      "text": "And the good side of that is that we can be a part of the solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 192100.0,
      "end_time": 194100.0,
      "text": "So what are we going to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 195140.0,
      "end_time": 199396.0,
      "text": "What can we do to chip away at polarization in everyday life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199420.0,
      "end_time": 203236.0,
      "text": "What could we do to connect with and communicate with"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 204980.0,
      "text": "our political counterparts?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 205540.0,
      "end_time": 209676.0,
      "text": "Well, these were exactly the questions that I and my colleague, Matt Feinberg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 209700.0,
      "end_time": 211558.0,
      "text": "became fascinated with a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211582.0,
      "end_time": 213781.0,
      "text": "and we started doing research on this topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214740.0,
      "end_time": 217716.0,
      "text": "And one of the first things that we discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 217740.0,
      "end_time": 221196.0,
      "text": "that I think is really helpful for understanding polarization"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221220.0,
      "end_time": 222436.0,
      "text": "is to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 222460.0,
      "end_time": 226876.0,
      "text": "that the political divide in our country is undergirded by a deeper moral divide."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226900.0,
      "end_time": 231676.0,
      "text": "So one of the most robust findings in the history of political psychology"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 231700.0,
      "end_time": 235396.0,
      "text": "is this pattern identified by Jon Haidt and Jesse Graham,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235420.0,
      "end_time": 236636.0,
      "text": "psychologists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 236660.0,
      "end_time": 240676.0,
      "text": "that liberals and conservatives tend to endorse different values"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 240700.0,
      "end_time": 241899.0,
      "text": "to different degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 242420.0,
      "end_time": 247916.0,
      "text": "So for example, we find that liberals tend to endorse values like equality"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247940.0,
      "end_time": 251596.0,
      "text": "and fairness and care and protection from harm"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 251620.0,
      "end_time": 253756.0,
      "text": "more than conservatives do."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253780.0,
      "end_time": 259360.0,
      "text": "And conservatives tend to endorse values like loyalty, patriotism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 259600.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262516.0,
      "text": "respect for authority and moral purity"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 262540.0,
      "end_time": 264620.0,
      "text": "more than liberals do."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 265740.0,
      "end_time": 269796.0,
      "text": "And Matt and I were thinking that maybe this moral divide"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269820.0,
      "end_time": 272916.0,
      "text": "might be helpful for understanding how it is"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 272940.0,
      "end_time": 275356.0,
      "text": "that liberals and conservatives talk to one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 275380.0,
      "end_time": 277796.0,
      "text": "and why they so often seem to talk past one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 277820.0,
      "end_time": 279360.0,
      "text": "when they do."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 279600.0,
      "end_time": 281360.0,
      "text": "So we conducted a study"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 281600.0,
      "end_time": 284156.0,
      "text": "where we recruited liberals to a study"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 284180.0,
      "end_time": 286636.0,
      "text": "where they were supposed to write a persuasive essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286660.0,
      "end_time": 291100.0,
      "text": "that would be compelling to a conservative in support of same-sex marriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 291620.0,
      "end_time": 294876.0,
      "text": "And what we found was that liberals tended to make arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 294900.0,
      "end_time": 299750.0,
      "text": "in terms of the liberal moral values of equality and fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 299100.0,
      "end_time": 300836.0,
      "text": "So they said things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 300860.0,
      "end_time": 304236.0,
      "text": "\"Everyone should have the right to love whoever they choose,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 306836.0,
      "text": "and, \"They\" -- they being gay Americans --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 306860.0,
      "end_time": 309620.0,
      "text": "\"deserve the same equal rights as other Americans.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 310180.0,
      "end_time": 313396.0,
      "text": "Overall, we found that 69 percent of liberals"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313420.0,
      "end_time": 318836.0,
      "text": "invoked one of the more liberal moral values in constructing their essay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 318860.0,
      "end_time": 322556.0,
      "text": "and only nine percent invoked one of the more conservative moral values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 322580.0,
      "end_time": 325996.0,
      "text": "even though they were supposed to be trying to persuade conservatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 326200.0,
      "end_time": 330316.0,
      "text": "And when we studied conservatives and had them make persuasive arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 330340.0,
      "end_time": 333236.0,
      "text": "in support of making English the official language of the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 335796.0,
      "text": "a classically conservative political position,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 335820.0,
      "end_time": 338360.0,
      "text": "we found that they weren&#39;t much better at this."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 338600.0,
      "end_time": 339676.0,
      "text": "59 percent of them made arguments"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 339700.0,
      "end_time": 342396.0,
      "text": "in terms of one of the more conservative moral values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 342420.0,
      "end_time": 344916.0,
      "text": "and just eight percent invoked a liberal moral value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 344940.0,
      "end_time": 348300.0,
      "text": "even though they were supposed to be targeting liberals for persuasion."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 349300.0,
      "end_time": 353340.0,
      "text": "Now, you can see right away why we&#39;re in trouble here. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 354100.0,
      "end_time": 357596.0,
      "text": "People&#39;s moral values, they&#39;re their most deeply held beliefs."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 357620.0,
      "end_time": 361200.0,
      "text": "People are willing to fight and die for their values."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 361540.0,
      "end_time": 364236.0,
      "text": "Why are they going to give that up just to agree with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 367796.0,
      "text": "on something that they don&#39;t particularly want to agree with you on anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 367820.0,
      "end_time": 371750.0,
      "text": "If that persuasive appeal that you&#39;re making to your Republican uncle"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371100.0,
      "end_time": 373516.0,
      "text": "means that he doesn&#39;t just have to change his view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 373540.0,
      "end_time": 375706.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s got to change his underlying values, too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 375730.0,
      "end_time": 377290.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not going to go very far."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 377900.0,
      "end_time": 379219.0,
      "text": "So what would work better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 380200.0,
      "end_time": 384316.0,
      "text": "Well, we believe it&#39;s a technique that we call moral reframing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 384340.0,
      "end_time": 386955.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve studied it in a series of experiments."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 386980.0,
      "end_time": 388476.0,
      "text": "In one of these experiments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 388500.0,
      "end_time": 391636.0,
      "text": "we recruited liberals and conservatives to a study"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 391660.0,
      "end_time": 393956.0,
      "text": "where they read one of three essays"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 393980.0,
      "end_time": 397200.0,
      "text": "before having their environmental attitudes surveyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 397460.0,
      "end_time": 398955.0,
      "text": "And the first of these essays"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 398980.0,
      "end_time": 402356.0,
      "text": "was a relatively conventional pro-environmental essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 402380.0,
      "end_time": 406396.0,
      "text": "that invoked the liberal values of care and protection from harm."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 406420.0,
      "end_time": 408956.0,
      "text": "It said things like, \"In many important ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 408980.0,
      "end_time": 411796.0,
      "text": "we are causing real harm to the places we live in,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 411820.0,
      "end_time": 414635.0,
      "text": "and, \"It is essential that we take steps now"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 414660.0,
      "end_time": 417580.0,
      "text": "to prevent further destruction from being done to our Earth.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 418940.0,
      "end_time": 420356.0,
      "text": "Another group of participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 420380.0,
      "end_time": 422596.0,
      "text": "were assigned to read a really different essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 422620.0,
      "end_time": 427600.0,
      "text": "that was designed to tap into the conservative value of moral purity."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 428100.0,
      "end_time": 429996.0,
      "text": "It was a pro-environmental essay as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 430200.0,
      "end_time": 431515.0,
      "text": "and it said things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 431540.0,
      "end_time": 435780.0,
      "text": "\"Keeping our forests, drinking water, and skies pure is of vital importance.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 436820.0,
      "end_time": 438316.0,
      "text": "\"We should regard the pollution"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 438340.0,
      "end_time": 440380.0,
      "text": "of the places we live in to be disgusting.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 440980.0,
      "end_time": 443760.0,
      "text": "And, \"Reducing pollution can help us preserve"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443100.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "what is pure and beautiful about the places we live.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 447700.0,
      "end_time": 449116.0,
      "text": "And then we had a third group"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 449140.0,
      "end_time": 451635.0,
      "text": "that were assigned to read just a nonpolitical essay."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 451660.0,
      "end_time": 454396.0,
      "text": "It was just a comparison group so we could get a baseline."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 454420.0,
      "end_time": 456373.0,
      "text": "And what we found when we surveyed people"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 456397.0,
      "end_time": 458596.0,
      "text": "about their environmental attitudes afterwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 458620.0,
      "end_time": 461556.0,
      "text": "we found that liberals, it didn&#39;t matter what essay they read."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 461580.0,
      "end_time": 464676.0,
      "text": "They tended to have highly pro-environmental attitudes regardless."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 464700.0,
      "end_time": 467116.0,
      "text": "Liberals are on board for environmental protection."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 467140.0,
      "end_time": 468356.0,
      "text": "Conservatives, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 468380.0,
      "end_time": 472796.0,
      "text": "were significantly more supportive of progressive environmental policies"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 472820.0,
      "end_time": 474356.0,
      "text": "and environmental protection"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 474380.0,
      "end_time": 476436.0,
      "text": "if they had read the moral purity essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 476460.0,
      "end_time": 478859.0,
      "text": "than if they read one of the other two essays."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 479980.0,
      "end_time": 483760.0,
      "text": "We even found that conservatives who read the moral purity essay"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 483100.0,
      "end_time": 486596.0,
      "text": "were significantly more likely to say that they believed in global warming"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 486620.0,
      "end_time": 488525.0,
      "text": "and were concerned about global warming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 488549.0,
      "end_time": 491275.0,
      "text": "even though this essay didn&#39;t even mention global warming."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 491300.0,
      "end_time": 493756.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s just a related environmental issue."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 493780.0,
      "end_time": 496859.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s how robust this moral reframing effect was."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 497780.0,
      "end_time": 501515.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve studied this on a whole slew of different political issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 501540.0,
      "end_time": 505276.0,
      "text": "So if you want to move conservatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 505300.0,
      "end_time": 508396.0,
      "text": "on issues like same-sex marriage or national health insurance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 508420.0,
      "end_time": 511876.0,
      "text": "it helps to tie these liberal political issues to conservative values"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 511900.0,
      "end_time": 514699.0,
      "text": "like patriotism and moral purity."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 515620.0,
      "end_time": 517716.0,
      "text": "And we studied it the other way, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 517740.0,
      "end_time": 521556.0,
      "text": "If you want to move liberals to the right on conservative policy issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 521580.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526196.0,
      "text": "like military spending and making English the official language of the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 526220.0,
      "end_time": 527876.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to be more persuasive"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 527900.0,
      "end_time": 531236.0,
      "text": "if you tie those conservative policy issues to liberal moral values"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 531260.0,
      "end_time": 533140.0,
      "text": "like equality and fairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 534460.0,
      "end_time": 537316.0,
      "text": "All these studies have the same clear message:"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 537340.0,
      "end_time": 540276.0,
      "text": "if you want to persuade someone on some policy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 540300.0,
      "end_time": 544140.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s helpful to connect that policy to their underlying moral values."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 545340.0,
      "end_time": 547516.0,
      "text": "And when you say it like that"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 547540.0,
      "end_time": 549360.0,
      "text": "it seems really obvious. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 549600.0,
      "end_time": 550835.0,
      "text": "Like, why did we come here tonight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 550860.0,
      "end_time": 552760.0,
      "text": "Why --"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 552100.0,
      "end_time": 553636.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 553660.0,
      "end_time": 555699.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s incredibly intuitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 557220.0,
      "end_time": 560516.0,
      "text": "And even though it is, it&#39;s something we really struggle to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 560540.0,
      "end_time": 564396.0,
      "text": "You know, it turns out that when we go to persuade somebody on a political issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 564420.0,
      "end_time": 567156.0,
      "text": "we talk like we&#39;re speaking into a mirror."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 567180.0,
      "end_time": 571555.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t persuade so much as we rehearse our own reasons"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 571580.0,
      "end_time": 574460.0,
      "text": "for why we believe some sort of political position."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 575220.0,
      "end_time": 579636.0,
      "text": "We kept saying when we were designing these reframed moral arguments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 579660.0,
      "end_time": 582300.0,
      "text": "\"Empathy and respect, empathy and respect.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 582860.0,
      "end_time": 584316.0,
      "text": "If you can tap into that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 584340.0,
      "end_time": 585996.0,
      "text": "you can connect"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 586200.0,
      "end_time": 588819.0,
      "text": "and you might be able to persuade somebody in this country."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 589380.0,
      "end_time": 591796.0,
      "text": "So thinking again"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 591820.0,
      "end_time": 594100.0,
      "text": "about what movie we&#39;re in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 595200.0,
      "end_time": 596596.0,
      "text": "maybe I got carried away before."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 596620.0,
      "end_time": 598580.0,
      "text": "Maybe it&#39;s not a zombie apocalypse movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 599340.0,
      "end_time": 601260.0,
      "text": "Maybe instead it&#39;s a buddy cop movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 601860.0,
      "end_time": 603876.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 603900.0,
      "end_time": 605915.0,
      "text": "Just roll with it, just go with it please."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 605940.0,
      "end_time": 607380.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 608300.0,
      "end_time": 610996.0,
      "text": "You know the kind: there&#39;s a white cop and a black cop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 611200.0,
      "end_time": 613156.0,
      "text": "or maybe a messy cop and an organized cop."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 613180.0,
      "end_time": 615236.0,
      "text": "Whatever it is, they don&#39;t get along"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 615260.0,
      "end_time": 616545.0,
      "text": "because of this difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 617340.0,
      "end_time": 620556.0,
      "text": "But in the end, when they have to come together and they cooperate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 620580.0,
      "end_time": 622516.0,
      "text": "the solidarity that they feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 622540.0,
      "end_time": 626180.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s greater because of that gulf that they had to cross. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 627100.0,
      "end_time": 629760.0,
      "text": "And remember that in these movies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 629100.0,
      "end_time": 631996.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s usually worst in the second act"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 632200.0,
      "end_time": 634420.0,
      "text": "when our leads are further apart than ever before."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 637596.0,
      "text": "And so maybe that&#39;s where we are in this country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 637620.0,
      "end_time": 639796.0,
      "text": "late in the second act of a buddy cop movie --"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 639820.0,
      "end_time": 642396.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 642420.0,
      "end_time": 645500.0,
      "text": "torn apart but about to come back together."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 647220.0,
      "end_time": 648876.0,
      "text": "It sounds good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 648900.0,
      "end_time": 650756.0,
      "text": "but if we want it to happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 650780.0,
      "end_time": 653500.0,
      "text": "I think the responsibility is going to start with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 654340.0,
      "end_time": 656500.0,
      "text": "So this is my call to you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 657300.0,
      "end_time": 659300.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s put this country back together."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 660900.0,
      "end_time": 663956.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do it despite the politicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 663980.0,
      "end_time": 666836.0,
      "text": "and the media and Facebook and Twitter"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 666860.0,
      "end_time": 668396.0,
      "text": "and Congressional redistricting"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 668420.0,
      "end_time": 671140.0,
      "text": "and all of it, all the things that divide us."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 672180.0,
      "end_time": 674420.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s do it because it&#39;s right."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 675740.0,
      "end_time": 680156.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s do it because this hate and contempt"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 680180.0,
      "end_time": 682339.0,
      "text": "that flows through all of us every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 683220.0,
      "end_time": 686396.0,
      "text": "makes us ugly and it corrupts us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 686420.0,
      "end_time": 689740.0,
      "text": "and it threatens the very fabric of our society."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 691780.0,
      "end_time": 694435.0,
      "text": "We owe it to one another and our country"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 694460.0,
      "end_time": 696620.0,
      "text": "to reach out and try to connect."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 697820.0,
      "end_time": 700980.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t afford to hate them any longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 702200.0,
      "end_time": 704220.0,
      "text": "and we can&#39;t afford to let them hate us either."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 705700.0,
      "end_time": 707600.0,
      "text": "Empathy and respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 707700.0,
      "end_time": 708940.0,
      "text": "Empathy and respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 709740.0,
      "end_time": 713540.0,
      "text": "If you think about it, it&#39;s the very least that we owe our fellow citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 714220.0,
      "end_time": 715436.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 715460.0,
      "end_time": 720145.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}